<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:18:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>焦点：贸易紧张局势加剧，中国风力涡轮机制造商进军欧洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/chinese-wind-turbine-makers-move-into-europe-trade-tensions-flare-2024-07-19/</link><description>中国风力涡轮机制造商本月在德国获得了第一笔订单，他们在欧洲市场上建立了势头，并加剧了欧盟行业对其面临生存威胁的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/chinese-wind-turbine-makers-move-into-europe-trade-tensions-flare-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>国际能源署表示，今年冷却需求的增长将使燃煤电厂保持在线状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/rising-cooling-demand-keep-coal-plants-online-this-year-iea-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>国际能源署 (IEA) 在周五的一份报告中表示，由于气温上升，空调需求增加，今年全球电力需求将以近 20 年来最快的速度增长。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 05:43:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/rising-cooling-demand-keep-coal-plants-online-this-year-iea-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>受中国市场拖累，电梯制造商迅达第二季度订单下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-order-intake-slips-second-quarter-weighed-by-china-2024-07-19/</link><description>瑞士电梯和自动扶梯制造商迅达周五报告称，由于中国建筑市场放缓对新安装量造成压力，第二季度订单量略有下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 04:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-order-intake-slips-second-quarter-weighed-by-china-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国官员预计高风险政策会议后的道路将崎岖不平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-officials-expect-bumpy-ride-economic-policy-2024-07-19/</link><description>中国官员周五承认，本周一次重要的共产党会议结束时再次强调的全面经济目标清单包含“许多复杂的矛盾”，这表明政策实施的道路崎岖不平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-officials-expect-bumpy-ride-economic-policy-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国将加快房地产业模式重塑工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-recovery-not-strong-enough-communist-party-official-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>一位负责金融和经济事务的党内高级官员周五表示，中国将加快房地产行业的重组工作，以消除以前的高债务、周转率和杠杆率等特征。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:23:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-recovery-not-strong-enough-communist-party-official-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>外长回应特朗普 台湾必须自力更生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-must-rely-itself-defence-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>外交部长林家龙周五在回应唐纳德·特朗普的批评时表示，台湾必须依靠自己进行防御，鉴于其面临来自中国的威胁，台湾可能会继续增加开支并实现军事现代化。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:56:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-must-rely-itself-defence-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国对美国丙酸产品启动反倾销税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-start-anti-dumping-duties-propionic-acid-products-us-2024-07-19/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，自7月21日起，对原产于美国的丙酸产品实施反倾销税，实施期限为5年。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-start-anti-dumping-duties-propionic-acid-products-us-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因科技股溃败蔓延和全球不确定性而暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-19/</link><description>尽管全球降息周期已经开始，但主要经济体的不确定性仍给投资者带来了阻力，亚洲股市本周将以低迷收盘。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>由于交易员权衡美国利率，美元预计每周上涨，日元稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/dollar-set-eke-out-weekly-gain-traders-weigh-us-rates-yen-wobbles-2024-07-19/</link><description>由于交易员思考美国利率前景，美元有望在周五结束连续两周的跌势，而日元在日本通胀连续第二个月加速后保持稳定，保持了加息的前景。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 01:49:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/dollar-set-eke-out-weekly-gain-traders-weigh-us-rates-yen-wobbles-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国在瓦努阿图开设大使馆，中国竞争的最新举措</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-opens-embassy-vanuatu-latest-step-china-competition-2024-07-18/</link><description>美国周四在太平洋岛国瓦努阿图开设大使馆，这是美国与中国长期争夺亚太地区影响力的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 22:59:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-opens-embassy-vanuatu-latest-step-china-competition-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着经济增长放缓，中国顽固的储户无视消费诱因</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stubborn-savers-ignore-inducements-spend-growth-slows-2024-07-18/</link><description>尽管家庭存款放缓且银行大幅降息，但中国的消费支出未能对政府措施做出反应，这表明规避风险的居民更愿意偿还债务并购买理财产品。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stubborn-savers-ignore-inducements-spend-growth-slows-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：科技风暴过后希望平静，日本消费者物价指数 (CPI) 着眼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-18/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国重申崇高的政策目标，但未提供实施细节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-industrial-modernisation-raft-other-reforms-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国领导人周四重申了广泛的经济政策目标，从工业现代化到扩大内需以及遏制债务和房地产行业风险，但没有详细说明实施步骤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-industrial-modernisation-raft-other-reforms-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对欧盟猪肉发起反倾销调查，点名丹麦、荷兰、西班牙企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-singles-out-danish-dutch-spanish-firms-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-pork-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国周四将丹麦皇冠公司以及荷兰和西班牙猪肉公司列为对欧盟猪肉进口进行反倾销调查的目标，北京方面加大了对欧盟限制其电动汽车出口的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-singles-out-danish-dutch-spanish-firms-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-pork-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国共产党罢免最高机构中前外长、国防部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，周四，在中国共产党最大的最高决策机构会议上，中国共产党将前外交部长和国防部长秦刚和李尚福撤出中央委员会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>